{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"83940e46cf","title":"中共中央关于地主富农加入供销合作社问题给西北局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd9adbe809","index":0,"year":1952,"month":5,"day":25,"articleId":"83940e46cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"acd4b50090","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于地主富农加入供销合作社问题给西北局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"b878e2d0eb","type":"appellation","text":"西北局并各中央局、分局并合作总社党组：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"0c62522ecb","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十日电悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"b163953c88","type":"paragraph","text":"关于地主富农加人供销合作社问题，同意西北局意见，但在执行步骤上应照以下各项办理。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"f4dc413f62","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）在土改前或土改后的很短时间内，开始组织供销社，基础薄弱，领导又缺乏经验的地区，以暂不吸收地主富农人社为宜。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"28b264d475","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）土改已经一定时间，供销社组织已较巩固，可吸收富农参加，但须经理事会通过，社员代表会议批准，人社后有选举权无被选举权，以免其篡夺领导。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"88874565ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）土改后的地主要求加入供销社，须经农民协会审查同意，理事会通过，社员代表会议批准，入社后无选举权和被选举权。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"},{"id":"579649c968","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央五月二十五日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf"}],"page":{"id":"0d32b6fbf5","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"83940e46cf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}